metadata.name: Unrevealed Hog Gang
metadata.description:
Hogs will automatically reveal after 5,000 minted or 48 hours.

From dirt to the streets these Hogs had to adapt. After years of being on the plate they decided it was time for them to serve up some revenge. Mean, ugly, and totally insane, these 10,000 unique characters have a lot of attitude and a dirty future ahead of them. Join the gang and grab a Hog Gang NFT while you still you can.
